{"id":"035b4802-319c-4410-befc-1e5eb8466abb","name":"Virestra The Imperial Steel Wing Commander","description":"<p>\"<strong>To command is to lead, to lead is to shield. And to shield Darastrix? That is an honor beyond words.”</strong><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 958px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/336161128726134785/1310320973496455229/0cee4194-6c0b-4bc4-bb31-be5b57f7db56.jpg?ex=6744cb00&amp;is=67437980&amp;hm=590440d7857e9d559f1c0b2058b43705f8a233862349b5d3582f3ef82ac00d82&amp;=\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/98068345-2edf-451c-96b4-e22c218593ff_50144048-534d-4cfb-ae27-0a65b10bfc31.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/98068345-2edf-451c-96b4-e22c218593ff_994e82aa-ffe0-4d2d-9784-f655230a821f.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Trigger Warnings</mark></span>: Violence, Possible Torture, Blood, Captivity, Prisoner, Death. Dead Dove Territory. <br><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/98068345-2edf-451c-96b4-e22c218593ff_d4ec8339-15de-4ba9-845b-7620643a8d72.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/qEqNwgAZQW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 251px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/98068345-2edf-451c-96b4-e22c218593ff_a388ae95-2edc-4243-a5b2-a9dd38279c49.webp?width=1000\"></a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/dantecornelius\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 214px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/98068345-2edf-451c-96b4-e22c218593ff_0a9c560d-82df-4568-ad4f-00c98df65773.webp?width=1000\"></a><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/98068345-2edf-451c-96b4-e22c218593ff_d4ec8339-15de-4ba9-845b-7620643a8d72.webp?width=1000\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(235, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">Creator Notes:</mark></strong></span></p><p><br>This is a slight departure from my planned Lightfury, and it’s been a long time since I've introduced another dragon, I know... but I hope you’ll love her! She came to me with inspiration, much like Xyraxis.I hope you can forgive me for leaving you without a proper character for so long, but I aim to make it up to you as I focus on my upcoming series.<br><br>Keep in mind, of some ussual JLLM issues like speaking for the user, misgendering, etc. And Like always please leave comments and chats i love all of them ^^ and stay Dragonlicious. ;)</p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Here is A 'Sister' Picture of Viresta and a Character made by a Friend of Mine. </strong><br><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/79a8ff66-7263-4094-a203-428db032df3a_profile-of-aquaplayer\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Aquaplayer</strong></a><br></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/79a8ff66-7263-4094-a203-428db032df3a_profile-of-aquaplayer\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" class=\"chakra-image css-hsi2ui\" style=\"width: 175px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"Avatar\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/avatars/79a8ff66-7263-4094-a203-428db032df3a_aaa34385-e8f9-46bb-aa98-d309853698eb.webp?width=600\"></a></h3><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9de9a6f3-997b-405d-954b-0bcafc8554e